						</svg>
						<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Mit Formalogix automatisiert:</h3>
					</div>
					<ul class="space-y-3 mb-6">
						<li class="flex items-start">
							<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
								<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
							</svg>
							<span class="text-gray-700"><strong>24-48 Stunden Durchlaufzeit</strong></span>
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start">
							<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
								<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
							</svg>
							<span class="text-gray-700"><strong>99,8% Genauigkeit</strong> durch Hybrid-Ansatz</span>
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start">
							<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
								<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
							</svg>
							<span class="text-gray-700"><strong>Skalierbar auf beliebige Mengen</strong></span>
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start">
							<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
								<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
							</svg>
							<span class="text-gray-700"><strong>Effiziente Ressourcennutzung</strong></span>
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start">
							<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
								<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
							</svg>
							<span class="text-gray-700"><strong>Daten sofort verfügbar</strong></span>
						</li>
					</ul>
					<div class="solution-highlight">
						<p class="text-sm text-gray-700 font-medium">
							Beispiel: 50.000 Formulare werden automatisiert verarbeitet
							mit garantierter Qualität und schneller Verfügbarkeit
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="text-center">
				<a href="#pricing" class="btn-primary inline-block">
					Berechnen Sie Ihr Einsparpotenzial
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Services Section -->
	<section id="services" class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
		<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
			<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-4 text-gray-900 scroll-reveal">Unsere Services</h2>
			<p class="text-center text-gray-600 mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto scroll-reveal">
				Wir bieten flexible Lösungen für jeden Bedarf - von Selbstbedienung bis zur maßgeschneiderten Enterprise-Lösung.
			</p>

			<div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
				<!-- Self-Service -->
				<div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 scroll-reveal">
					<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-formalogix-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
						<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-formalogix-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2 text-gray-900">Volle Kontrolle. Volle Transparenz.</h3>
					<p class="text-sm text-formalogix-600 font-semibold mb-4">Für Teams, die Technologie beherrschen wollen, nicht umgekehrt.</p>
					<p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
						Unsere Self-Service Plattform gibt Ihnen die Werkzeuge, die bisher nur mit enormem Entwicklungsaufwand möglich waren.
					</p>
					<ul class="space-y-3 mb-8">
						<li class="flex items-start">
							<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-formalogix-500 mr-2 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
								<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
							</svg>
							<span class="text-sm text-gray-600">API-First-Architektur für nahtlose Integration</span>
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start">
							<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-formalogix-500 mr-2 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
								<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
							</svg>
							<span class="text-sm text-gray-600">Echtzeit-Dashboard für komplette Prozesstransparenz</span>
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start">
							<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-formalogix-500 mr-2 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
								<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
							</svg>
							<span class="text-sm text-gray-600">Sie kontrollieren Timing, Volumen und Datenfluss</span>
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start">
							<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-formalogix-500 mr-2 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
								<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
							</svg>
							<span class="text-sm text-gray-600">Keine Black Box – Sie sehen jeden Schritt der KI-Analyse</span>
						</li>
					</ul>
					<a href="https://app.formalogix.com" class="block text-center bg-formalogix-500 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-formalogix-600 transition-colors">
						Kostenlos testen
					</a>
				</div>

				<!-- Full-Service -->
				<div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 border-2 border-formalogix-500 relative scroll-reveal">
					<div class="absolute -top-4 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 bg-formalogix-500 text-white px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">
						Beliebt
					</div>
					<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-formalogix-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
						<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-formalogix-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 3v4M3 5h4M6 17v4m-2-2h4m5-16l2.286 6.857L21 12l-5.714 2.143L13 21l-2.286-6.857L5 12l5.714-2.143L13 3z" />
